    When I set text to "<text>"
    Then Multi Action Button text on preview is set to "<text>"
    Examples:
      | text                    |
      | Sample text             |
      | 1234567890              |
      | áéíóú¿¡üñ               |
      | !@#$%^*()_+-=~[];:.,?{} |
      | ÄÖÜßäöüß                |
